org.treetank.node.delegates

Class ValNodeDelegate

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.treetank.node.delegates.ValNodeDelegate
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    INode, IValNode

    public class ValNodeDelegate
extends Object
implements IValNode
    Delegate method for all nodes containing \"value\"-data. That means that independent values are stored by the nodes delegating the calls of the interface IValNode to this class.
    Author:
    Sebastian Graf, University of Konstanz
